            <offset>0</offset>
            <sentence>
                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>﻿The proband, a boy, was the first child of healthy unrelated parents (a 25-year-old mother and a 29-year-old father at the time of delivery).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>143</offset>
                <text>Family history was unremarkable.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>176</offset>
                <text>He was born at term by forceps for continued failure to progress.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>242</offset>
                <text>Weight was 2.750 kg (10th centile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>278</offset>
                <text>Apgar score was normal, despite the presence of a small cephalohematoma in his left parietal regions.</text>
                <annotation id="1">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0012541</infon>
                    <location length="15" offset="56"/>
                    <text>cephalohematoma</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>380</offset>
                <text>Neonatal moderate hypotonia and poor sucking were interpreted as the mild and temporary effects of the instrumental delivery.</text>
                <annotation id="2">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0001252</infon>
                    <location length="9" offset="18"/>
                    <text>hypotonia</text>
                </annotation>
                <annotation id="3">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
                    <infon key="HPOterm">http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/HP_0002033</infon>
                    <location length="12" offset="32"/>
                    <text>poor sucking</text>
                </annotation>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>506</offset>
                <text>In effect, developmental milestones were not delayed, although during subsequent years he experienced great and increased learning and behavior difficulties due to an inattentive, hyperactive, and impulsive conduct.</text>
